{"tid":2457656,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–細菌也懂得乘坐順風車","createTime":"2021-03-22T22:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T05:49:44.000Z","uid":38861,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d43f4a774399bd2fcb84e5566d43d75f31a10a75","tid":2457656,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T22:51:42.000Z","msg":"Streptomyces 是一種能夠為植物提供良好保護的細菌，它們駐紮在植物的根部，釋放出不同的物質及抗生素，消滅泥土間對植物有害的細菌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXYbXTe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXYbXTe.jpg&h=4297cd4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是，Streptomyces 已知是一種不懂得自我移動的細菌，它們到底是如何抵達植物根部的呢?<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）雖然Streptomyces 並不懂得自我移動，但它的嬰兒形態(Spore)可以黏附在懂得自我移動的細菌的鞭毛之上，搭順風車在泥土之間行走。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fkQJOZW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfkQJOZW.png&h=f11127b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）研究更發現，Streptomyces spore 是依靠其表面名為Rodlein的蛋白質與其他細菌的鞭毛作出黏貼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8nh4yrF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8nh4yrF.png&h=c9af9ca9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n若果失去Rodlein蛋白質的話，那些Spore亦會因而失去搭順風車的能力。<br />\n由此可相信，這是其中一道Streptomyces抵達植物根部的機制。<br />\n<br />\n現時多國已打開大門讓各Spore前往理想之地，是否願意往外闖一闖抵達植物根部，還是留守原地等運到，一切也是你的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXA6WLWD%2BvnO7xCw116w%2BR6c%3D&h=32192a7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXA6WLWD%2BvnO7xCw116w%2BR6c%3D&h=761d6b02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41396-021-00952-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41396-021-00952-8&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXA6WLWD%2BvnO7xCw116w%2BR6c%3D&h=ba85c389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41396-021-00952-8</a>"},{"pid":"1b3c89c7629d74660021496161b4be8451335225","tid":2457656,"uid":24523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T22:52:42.000Z","msg":"早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec7a38ebfe93a3cf349a9a6643e82b2410abf95","tid":2457656,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b3c89c7629d74660021496161b4be8451335225","tid":2457656,"uid":24523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T22:52:42.000Z","msg":"早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T22:53:16.000Z","msg":"早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18cdb90193247b360a67405f81096a51e4d1de18","tid":2457656,"uid":201303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:25:11.000Z","msg":"好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog